            "text": " .b- The octahedron. It has  $2^n$  facets, each of them is a regular simplex of volume  $|F|_{n-1} = \\frac{\\sqrt{n}}{(n-1)!}$ .  Let  $\\Delta_k$  denote a regular k-simplex with edge length  $\\sqrt{2}$  (so  $|\\Delta_k|_k = \\frac{\\sqrt{k+1}}{k!}$ ). Then, if  $n \\geq 3$ :",
